</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-9848D934-FF3E-4AC9-BA07-69028FA44036" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note><note type="important" id="GUID-985FFBF4-CACE-47F4-AF21-7A7BEBBB34EA" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Use an antistatic wrist strap. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="FIG_95AE52A3FFA34A5BAF1ECF61A72EDA2D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-327382AC-4FC7-477B-9611-5BC5F562342A-low.png" id="IMAGE_E83BEE150449442DB5B0DB1BD84FCCB7" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-327382AC-4FC7-477B-9611-5BC5F562342A-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_676D8E59167F4927BAACAD2565440469" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_FDD8FD89D6E5405B860B62D2D8C2CE6D" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Disconnect the connector. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_AEBB46DB017744F6910C930D842EE074" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D5379A5E-123B-4809-84F8-B33B63C32B18-low.png" id="IMAGE_EFE81140D304435D8478BBC9ADE667CD" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D5379A5E-123B-4809-84F8-B33B63C32B18-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the safety switch (2 screws) of the manual maintenance door. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_72BFB19AFAC44C1DBBDA0E0DCBB5B26F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4F995529-3837-4D7B-9184-60B2C102C72A-low.png" id="IMAGE_D2C33A656C4644218A0955E4C87A763E" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4F995529-3837-4D7B-9184-60B2C102C72A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the lower left and lower right screws (2x) 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Loosen the upper left and right screws 
</p></li></ul><note type="caution" id="GUID-0539E4E7-0570-46D3-8B22-747A7CEC60C9" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Hold the unit so it does not drop. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-ACA8F0AF-1ACA-459F-941D-248C4B8DE7A1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-9C7CE79B-F0F2-4E38-A055-59D9478EC88C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9C7CE79B-F0F2-4E38-A055-59D9478EC88C-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-42B858EC-36D8-4C9A-834D-0BB1C5C6F058" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-443F0192-685C-4E3B-9DC3-B665E2EE552D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-443F0192-685C-4E3B-9DC3-B665E2EE552D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Take the unit and slide it out of the profile in the printer. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_CB68845F6B364A89972C2457BB71C2D5" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-BD0D1682-0C1B-4A7F-9200-F671E7D62877-low.png" id="IMAGE_C0D722CCCC2447E2BF3E23EEEAD0E7DF" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-BD0D1682-0C1B-4A7F-9200-F671E7D62877-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_A7B7F2276EC64F88A303AD9C9A521E96" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Push the frame at the right hand side to the arrow direction. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Now tighten bolt [A]. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_BD2AC32C03414C2F8B8CD1134D78185C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B658E256-CCF3-481F-9CCE-A845EB60FE29-low.png" id="IMAGE_05919EDAA2B04FD9A3AEB402A85C4960" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B658E256-CCF3-481F-9CCE-A845EB60FE29-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_C677EDFFAEA94DE993F91001D44F8EAD" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1ECEDA97-24FF-4DD1-B57D-85220BD0F13A-low.png" id="IMAGE_D44490BA60C64587B7C7FCCBEC48E51A" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1ECEDA97-24FF-4DD1-B57D-85220BD0F13A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Push the frame at the left hand side to the arrow direction. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Now tighten bolt [B]. 
